Permutation test for adonis under reduced model
Terms added sequentially (first to last)
Permutation: free
Number of permutations: 10000

vegan::adonis2(formula = distance(phyloseq_rel_nz, method = "horn") ~ sample_type * treatment + subject_id, data = phyloseq_rel_nz %>% sample_data %>% data.frame(check.names = F), permutations = 10000)
